name: Honesti
overview:
Honesti is a website which saves you a lot of money you spend for paid memberships on Indian matrimonial websites like shaadi.com, bharatmatrimony.com, jeevansathi.com and simplymarry.com.

Using Honesti users can contact any profile for free.

Honesti provides additional features like adding voice to your existing profile. For example if you have a shaadi.com profile then you can add voice to it.

Lastly Honesti rewards its members by posting free ads on Times of India and paying portion of paid memberships.
